Class Rocket

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.fel.pjv.Model.Entity.Entity
cz.cvut.fel.pjv.Model.Entity.Rocket
public class Rocket extends Entity
Rocket fired from rocket launcher by the player. The rocket is programmed so that it explodes on contact with enemy soldier or tower or after a time delay. the rocket then deals damage in the explosion area for 0.1 secs.
